        <div class="h2-title-box">
          <h2>부설기관<strong>산학협력단</strong><strong>연구진흥팀</strong></h2>
          <div class="contents-util">
			<a class="jwxe_a_zoom_in jw-relative jwnossl" id="jwxe_zoomIn" href="#zoom-in">글자확대</a>
